        "subject": "LU-19323 tests: add lnet-selftest test smoke into IPv6 except list",
        "message": "LU-19323 tests: add lnet-selftest test smoke into IPv6 except list\n\nThis patch temporarily adds lnet-selftest test smoke into\nthe IPv6 except list.\n\nIt also removes the NETTYPE check from sanity-lnet.sh because\nthe NETTYPE has already been checked from load_lnet()\nin test-framework.sh.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial mdtcount=4 mdscount=2 \\\n  env=FORCE_LARGE_NID=true,SANITY_LNET_EXCEPT=\"250\" \\\n  testlist=lnet-selftest,sanity-lnet\n\nChange-Id: I676bd3e1932e5b928426cd0a73226b0409e73204\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <yujian@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/61747\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: James Simmons <jsimmons@infradead.org>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Serguei Smirnov <ssmirnov@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
